Class PrincipalAttributeMultifactorAuthenticationPolicyEventResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apereo.cas.web.flow.resolver.impl.AbstractCasWebflowEventResolver
      • org.apereo.cas.web.flow.authentication.BaseMultifactorAuthenticationProviderEventResolver
        • org.apereo.cas.web.flow.resolver.impl.mfa.PrincipalAttributeMultifactorAuthenticationPolicyEventResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apereo.cas.services.MultifactorAuthenticationProviderResolver, CasWebflowEventResolver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PredicatedPrincipalAttributeMultifactorAuthenticationPolicyEventResolver

    public class PrincipalAttributeMultifactorAuthenticationPolicyEventResolver
extends BaseMultifactorAuthenticationProviderEventResolver
    This is PrincipalAttributeMultifactorAuthenticationPolicyEventResolver that attempts to locate a principal attribute, match its value against the provided pattern and decide the next event in the flow for the given service.
    Since:
    5.0.0
